<sect1 id="dir_326351fd6fbd1ed4d80f0b2b180f7c49_1autotoc_md277">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::scoring::commands</title><para>Score update commands for the command buffer.</para>
<para>This namespace contains command classes used to request score updates through the command system.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_326351fd6fbd1ed4d80f0b2b180f7c49_1autotoc_md278">
